$$ Simple PokémonLang Program
$$ Calculate and display health status

Move EmptyBall StartBattle fob fcb OpenBall
    $$ Variable declarations
    Pikachu health evo 100 dot
    Pikachu maxHealth evo 150 dot
    Charizard percentage evo 66.7 dot
    Togepi isHealthy evo 1 dot
    
    $$ Check health status
    Brock fob health > 80 fcb OpenBall
        pikapika fob "Excellent health!" fcb dot
    CloseBall Misty fob health >= 50 fcb OpenBall
        pikapika fob "Good health" fcb dot
    CloseBall Jessie OpenBall
        pikapika fob "Critical!" fcb dot
    CloseBall
    
    $$ Loop example
    Pikachu counter evo 0 dot
    WildBattle fob counter < 5 fcb OpenBall
        counter evo counter atk 1 dot
    CloseBall
    
    $$ Math operations
    Pikachu damage evo 10 x 5 dot
    Pikachu remaining evo health dmg damage dot
    
    back 0 dot
CloseBall
